dc_title_s: 2011 National Household Survey, Dissemination Area (DA) Level [semi-custom tabulation]
dc_description_s: This data contains  semi custom tabulations of the 2011 National Household Survey Profiles for various geographies including Canada, Provinces, Territories, Census Divisions, Census Subdivisions and Dissemination Areas. Some of the tabulations include the Federal Electoral Districts (2003 Representation Order) and/or Census Agglomerations.
